data.meta_description: A New Account of the East Indies Hamilton vol 1 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document summarizes a book that was digitized by Google to preserve the information and make it accessible. The book provides descriptions of the situations, products, customs, religions, and trade of countries between the Cape of Good Hope and Japan, based on the author's 30 years of residence in those areas. It also relates historical events from the past century in those regions.
